@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ugfeox(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.71)))
    v2 = wp.exp((0.91 / wp.cos(v0 + 0.12)))
    v2 = v0
    tmp = 0.75
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos((tmp + 0.21 + v0 + 0.90)))
    data[tid] = v0
